 <span data-ttu-id="2cb79-271">次の例を作成、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter>し、一部のプロパティを設定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2cb79-271">The following example creates a <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
